{"type": "article", "id": 13253, "title": "折纸台灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-10T08:03:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110827Mt7w8AfNIYDWv1z5.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t“折纸”一直是很多设计师感兴趣的概念，于是我们常常看到许多折纸式的设计。巴塞罗那设计工作室 Obvious 最近推出了一款折纸式的台灯，灯身采用的是不锈钢材料，灯光亮起来时，光影的变化会让整个灯看起来非常美丽。这是<a href=\"https://www.barcelonaindesign.com/designer/obvious/\" target=\"_blank\">设计工作室的主页</a>，他们致力于用常见的材料做简单的日常物件，走极简风格，点击可以查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261408324MGxgPBsy7ZkecCW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6575\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140833nglTjAKz9QkfMRbi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6575\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140833NElJzUPt5VYv27H4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3325\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614083381usafOdiZvG4w6D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}